OL,3,C'My hardest decision' - Trent
OL,4,CAlexander-Arnold to leave Liverpool
OL,6,FTrent Alexander-Arnold has announced
OL,7,Fhe will leave Liverpool when his
OL,8,Fcontract expires at the end of the
OL,9,Fseason.
OL,11,FThe England defender has been heavily
OL,12,Flinked with a free transfer to Real
OL,13,FMadrid.
OL,15,F"After 20 years at Liverpool Football
OL,16,FClub, now is the time for me to
OL,17,Fconfirm that I will be leaving at the
OL,18,Fend of the season," he posted on X.
OL,20,F"This is easily the hardest decision
OL,21,FI've ever made in my life."
