OL,4,CAlexander-Arnold to leave Liverpool
OL,6,FIt's understood that Arne Slot was
OL,7,Finformed of the player's decision in
OL,8,Fearly spring.
OL,10,FLiverpool previously rejected an offer
OL,11,Ffor Alexander-Arnold from a rival club
OL,12,F` believed to be Real Madrid ` as they
OL,13,Fdid not wish to lose a key player
OL,14,Fduring their quest to become champions.
