OL,3,C'My hardest decision' - Trent
OL,4,CAlexander-Arnold to leave Liverpool
OL,6,F"This decision is about experiencing a
OL,7,Fnew challenge, taking myself out of my
OL,8,Fcomfort zone and pushing myself both
OL,9,Fprofessionally and personally,"
OL,10,Fcontinued Alexander-Arnold, who will
OL,11,Fremain a valued member of Liverpool's
OL,12,Fsquad for the remainder of the
OL,13,Fcampaign.
OL,15,F"I've given my all every single day
OL,16,FI've been at this club, and I hope you
OL,17,Ffeel like I've given back to you
OL,18,Fduring my time here."
